# Signal CRM — Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# ── Legacy URL redirects ──────────────────────────────────────
/home       /           301
/signin     /login/     301
/register   /login/     301
/app        /dashboard/ 301

# ── SPA fallback — must be LAST ───────────────────────────────
# All unmatched paths → index.html with 200 (not 301)
# This lets Next.js client-side router handle all routes
/*          /index.html 200
